    Let me know if this is a possibility.

    All the best,
    Geoff

property.name: Bunny Island (2025)
property.address: 55A Hatherley Rd, MacTier

taskDescription:
-we have some tiny ant activity in the kitchen . Seems to be a yearly event. The exterminators are coming this Thursday May 29th to spray etc. Please have the team keep an eye out for ants. I found them in the top spice cabinet. I have ant spray for them to use if they need to. 

-have them take the top sheet covers off of all the beds. We will not be needing them for the summer. 

-replace the winter blankets at the foot of the bed to the summer quilts. Each room has its own quilt matching quilt

-make sure they lock the balcony doors. All doors. The balcony door in the quest bedroom was unlocked .

-we had and electrical wire burn that caught fire in the family room cabinet (where the puzzles are stored) this winter. Thank  God it wasnt worse . It was a miracle.  This is the hard  rule going forward. All light fixtures, lamps chandeliers must be shut off when they leave the cottage from each individual main lamp switch. Most of our lamps have a dimmer attached. Tell them not to touch the dimmers, only the light switch on and off. Sometimes the dimmers are so low that it is difficult to see that the light is on.

-there might be some weeks that we cant make it up. Those are the weeks thay they will have time to  go into drawers/ cabinets ,and of course dusting etc as usual.
